Class DataRowSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.plexobject.dp.domain.DataRowSet

  • public class DataRowSet
extends java.lang.Object
    This class abstracts set of rows that would represent collection of objects. Note that you can have rowset within a row to create nested structures
